{"_id":"jSs8crrwXg9R8H7h","name":"Sentinel","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"class","data":{"description":{"value":"“My will cannot break, but your body can.”\n<p>A sentinel is a warrior of steel and determination, using their iron will and training to withstand blows that would crush weaker warriors. Masters of defense, sentinels live to hold the line, guarding others against fatal blows while delivering punishment all her own. To a sentinel, there is nothing stronger than a warrior and their armor, forming a bond that can weather magical assaults and impossible odds regardless of what stands in their way. The might of a sentinel is not to be underestimated, as they are the pillars upon which armies are built.</p>\n<p><strong>Starting Wealth:</strong> 5d6 &#215; 10 gp (average 175 gp). In addition, each character begins play with an outfit worth 10 gp or less.</p>\n<p><strong>Starting Age:</strong> Self-taught</p>\n<p><strong>Role:</strong> A sentinel stands in the thick of battle, absorbing punishment and defending those weaker than herself.</p>\n<p><strong>Alignment:</strong> Any</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Die:</strong> d12</p>\n<p><strong>Class Skills:</strong> The Sentinel&#8217;s class skills are Bluff (Cha), Climb (Str), Craft (Int), Diplomacy (Cha), Handle Animal (Cha), Heal (Wis), Intimidate (Cha), Knowledge (nobility) (Int), Perception (Wis), Profession (Wis), Ride (Dex), Sense Motive (Wis), and Swim (Str).</p>\n<p><strong>Skill Ranks Per Level:</strong> 4 + Int modifier.</p>\n<p><strong>Proficiencies:</strong> Sentinels are proficient with simple weapons, as well as light armor and bucklers. In addition, if this is this character&#8217;s first level in any class, they may select a martial tradition of their choice.</p>\n\n<h2>Combat Training</h2>\n<p>A sentinel may combine combat spheres and talents to create powerful martial techniques. Sentinels are considered Expert practitioners and use Wisdom as their practitioner modifier.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"links":{"children":[],"classAssociations":[{"id":"spheres-sheet.som-class-abilities.wwHPoKUuiuJP9aWJ","dataType":"compendium","name":"Defender’s Soul","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":0},{"id":"spheres-sheet.som-class-abilities.JKBuQwBr2WeLEVkI","dataType":"compendium","name":"Guardian Challenge","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":1},{"id":"spheres-sheet.som-class-abilities.LWxfymlTNQ9ADWAd","dataType":"compendium","name":"Sentinel’s Reserve","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":2},{"id":"spheres-sheet.som-class-abilities.y4xTVESaaMy92eMV","dataType":"compendium","name":"Wise Reflexes","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":3},{"id":"spheres-sheet.som-class-abilities.GXio15q6Bi0OnH2B","dataType":"compendium","name":"Guard Wall","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":2,"_index":4},{"id":"spheres-sheet.som-class-abilities.rg8oDD7r0CaCuxoO","dataType":"compendium","name":"Dedicated Defense","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":2,"_index":5},{"id":"spheres-sheet.som-class-abilities.Gt5sxzVa5pQgTkuB","dataType":"compendium","name":"Second Wind","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":3,"_index":6},{"id":"spheres-sheet.som-class-abilities.fzYvpFw9Z1JAVQzd","dataType":"compendium","name":"Sentinel’s Imposition","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":4,"_index":7},{"id":"spheres-sheet.som-class-abilities.4gNci8JaV6KmVH46","dataType":"compendium","name":"Opportunistic Offense","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":5,"_index":8},{"id":"spheres-sheet.som-class-abilities.DnJvBLN35oOWRnl6","dataType":"compendium